<template>
  <Datatable tableName="Products" :columns="headList" :dataList="dataList"/>

<script>
import Datatable from '@/components/Datatable'
import axios from 'axios';

export default {
    name: 'Table',
    components: {
        Datatable
    },
    data() {
      return {
        headList: [
          { label: '_id'},
          { label: 'Name' },
          { label: 'Description' },
          { label: 'Type' },
          { label: 'Stock' },
          { label: 'Status' } 
        ],
        dataList: []
      }
    },   
    beforeCreate(){
    axios.get('http://192.168.100.212:3000/muqeet')
      .then((result) => {
        var value = result.data
        this.dataList= value
        console.log(value)
      }).catch((err) => {
        console.log(err)
      });
  } 
}
</script>
